<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Healthcare Asset Manager</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 15px;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: white;
        }
        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .hero button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #007bff;
            background-color: white;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .hero button:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .features div {
            text-align: center;
            width: 30%;
        }
        .features div img {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
        }
        .features div h3 {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Healthcare Asset Manager</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/assets">Manage Assets</a>
            <a href="/workorders">Work Orders</a>
            <a href="/auth/login">Login</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h2>Streamline Your Healthcare Equipment Management</h2>
        <p>Manage your assets and work orders efficiently with our simple yet powerful platform.</p>
        <button onclick="location.href='/login'">Get Started</button>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" alt="Asset Management">
            <h3>Manage Assets</h3>
            <p>Keep track of all your healthcare equipment in one place.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" alt="Work Orders">
            <h3>Track Work Orders</h3>
            <p>Easily create, assign, and track work orders.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" alt="Compliance">
            <h3>Ensure Compliance</h3>
            <p>Stay compliant with regulations and maintenance schedules.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Healthcare Asset Manager. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
